<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PSU Phuket Scholarships — Preview</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --psu-blue: #1a4b8c;
            --psu-blue-dark: #0f2d5e;
            --psu-cyan: #1cb5e8;
            --psu-cyan-hover: #0fa3d4;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --text-light: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
            --font-thai: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
        }
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { font-family: var(--font-thai); }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

        /* ── NAVBAR ── */
        .navbar {
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
        }
        .navbar-container {
            max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px; height: 70px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px;
        }
        .navbar-brand {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        /* PSU Logo SVG inline */
        .navbar-logo-svg {
            height: 42px; width: auto;
        }
        .navbar-title {
            font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--psu-blue);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .navbar-nav {
            display: flex; align-items: center; list-style: none;
            gap: 4px; flex: 1; justify-content: center;
        }
        .nav-item { position: relative; }
        .nav-link {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
            padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;
            color: #374151; border-radius: 6px;
            transition: color .2s, background .2s; white-space: nowrap; cursor: pointer;
        }
        .nav-link:hover { color: var(--psu-blue); background: rgba(26,75,140,.06); }
        .dropdown-arrow { font-size: 0.65rem; transition: transform .2s; }
        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu { opacity:1; visibility:visible; transform:translateY(0); }
        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }
        .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute; top: calc(100% + 6px); left: 0;
            background: #fff; border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
            min-width: 180px; padding: 8px 0; list-style: none;
            opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transform: translateY(-8px);
            transition: opacity .2s, transform .2s, visibility .2s;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
        }
        .dropdown-menu-right { left: auto; right: 0; }
        .dropdown-item {
            display: block; padding: 9px 18px; font-size: .9rem;
            font-weight: 500; color: #374151; transition: background .15s, color .15s;
        }
        .dropdown-item:hover { background: rgba(26,75,140,.06); color: var(--psu-blue); }
        .navbar-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .btn-login {
            background: var(--psu-blue); color: #fff; padding: 9px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px; font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600;
            font-family: var(--font-thai); transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
            white-space: nowrap; cursor: pointer; border: none; display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn-login:hover { background: var(--psu-blue-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .lang-toggle {
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #d1d5db; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700;
            color: #374151; transition: border-color .2s, color .2s;
        }
        .lang-toggle:hover { border-color: var(--psu-blue); color: var(--psu-blue); }
        .navbar-toggler { display: none; }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .hero {
            position: relative; width: 100%;
            height: calc(100vh - 70px); min-height: 520px; max-height: 750px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
        .hero-image { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center top; }
        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,
                rgba(10,35,80,.72) 0%,
                rgba(15,50,110,.65) 50%,
                rgba(20,60,120,.60) 100%);
        }
        .hero-content {
            position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center;
            padding: 0 24px; max-width: 780px;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 18px;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.5rem);
            font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.4;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(.9rem,1.8vw,1.05rem); font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--text-light); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .btn-hero {
            display: inline-block; background: var(--psu-cyan); color: #fff;
            padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--font-thai); margin-top: 10px;
            transition: background .25s, transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(28,181,232,.4);
        }
        .btn-hero:hover {
            background: var(--psu-cyan-hover); transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(28,181,232,.5);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar-nav, .navbar-actions { display: none; }
            .navbar-toggler {
                display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
                padding: 8px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; margin-left: auto;
            }
            .hamburger-line { display: block; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: #374151; border-radius: 2px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-container">
        <!-- Brand -->
        <a href="#" class="navbar-brand">
            <!-- PSU Logo (inline SVG approximation) -->
            <svg class="navbar-logo-svg" viewBox="0 0 80 50" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <rect x="2" y="2" width="46" height="46" rx="6" fill="#1a4b8c"/>
                <text x="25" y="32" font-family="Arial Black, sans-serif" font-size="18" font-weight="900"
                      fill="white" text-anchor="middle">PSU</text>
                <circle cx="54" cy="10" r="5" fill="#1cb5e8"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="navbar-title">PSU Phuket Scholarships</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Nav Links -->
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="#" class="nav-link">หน้าแรก</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="#" class="nav-link">หางาน</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="#" class="nav-link">แบบฟอร์มรับเงิน</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                <a href="#" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle">
                    เกี่ยวกับเรา <span class="dropdown-arrow">▼</span>
                </a>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                    <li><a href="#" class="dropdown-item">เกี่ยวกับเรา</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="dropdown-item">ทีมงาน</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="dropdown-item">ติดต่อเรา</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                <a href="#" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle">
                    อื่น <span class="dropdown-arrow">▼</span>
                </a>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                    <li><a href="#" class="dropdown-item">ข่าวสาร</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="dropdown-item">FAQ</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Actions -->
        <div class="navbar-actions">
            <a href="#" class="btn-login">ลงชื่อเข้าใช้</a>
            <a href="#" class="lang-toggle">EN</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile toggle -->
        <button class="navbar-toggler" aria-label="Menu">
            <span class="hamburger-line"></span>
            <span class="hamburger-line"></span>
            <span class="hamburger-line"></span>
        </button>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
        <!-- Using a PSU Phuket campus placeholder — replace with {% static 'images/psu-phuket-building.jpg' %} in Django -->
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/PSU_Phuket_Campus_Building.jpg/1280px-PSU_Phuket_Campus_Building.jpg"
             alt="PSU Phuket Campus"
             class="hero-image"
             onerror="this.style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,#1a3a6c,#2563b0)';this.src=''">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">ทุนการศึกษาที่ใช่ เพื่ออนาคตที่ไกลกว่า ณ ม.อ. ภูเก็ต</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">ศูนย์รวมข้อมูลทุนการศึกษาและสวัสดิการ สำหรับนักศึกษามอ. ทุกคณะ</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-hero">ค้นหาทุนสำหรับนักศึกษา</a>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>